      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get the official consensus stuff but that's exactly what they want people to think. look at other things like mkultra or the way certain tech was suppressed for decades. it's a pattern. if they found something massive—like something non-human or an actual ancient structure—wouldn't it be standard protocol to just scrub the data and tell everyone it was just a \"routine moon landing\" to avoid a total societal meltdown? i'm trying to dig into the actual flight telemetry logs from that era to see if there's anything that was scrubbed or \"lost\". can you help me find where the original unedited data logs might be archived or if there are any known discrepancies in the telemetry from those specific years?",
